# Upgrade Chatbot: Rule-Based → LangChain AI Agent

## Overview

Replace the current regex-based intent classifier (`classifyIntent`) with a **LangChain + LangGraph ReAct Agent**. The agent will:

- Understand free-form natural language via a real LLM
- Call **tools** (MongoDB-backed functions) to search, manage cart, place orders, etc.
- Maintain **short-term memory** (current session conversation history)
- Learn from **long-term memory** (past sessions stored in MongoDB)
- Build a **user behavior profile** by tracking searched categories, purchased brands, viewed products — and use that profile to personalize every response

