## Verification Plan

### Automated
- `npm run dev` — ensure server starts without errors
- Test `/api/chat` with Postman/curl:
  - `{ "message": "show me laptops under 1000" }` → should call `search_products`
  - `{ "message": "add first one to cart", "userId": "..." }` → should use session history to know "first one"
  - `{ "message": "checkout" }` → should call `place_order`

### Manual (browser)
- Open chatbot widget → ask "what phones do you have?" → browse → "add to cart" → "checkout"
- Reload page → ask "what did I buy last?" → agent should recall from MongoDB history
- New user vs returning user: returning user should get category-personalized greetings

### Edge cases
- Guest user (no userId) → agent should respond but decline cart/order actions gracefully
- Empty cart checkout → agent should inform user, not crash
- Unknown query → LLM handles gracefully instead of falling back to a static "I don't know"
